snippet.title: NHL 2000 Intro | ''Push It''
snippet.description:
One of the best openings to date for an EA Sports Hockey Game.

NHL 2000 was one of the last hockey games to be released for the PS1, leading into the new gen PS2 with NHL 2001.

This game is a great reason to own a PSOne or a PS2.
